Dear Athletes,

Let's compete again in the best place!

Welcome to Torun for the 15th European Masters Athletics Championships Indoor 2026.

Registrations are open from November 1 2025 until February 8 2026, at 23:59GMT (no late entries accepted).

On this platform you can buy the cancellation policy (if you decide to withdraw - but only before the registration deadline -we will refund the registration fee)

If you want have a look at the merchandise items: https://emaci2026.com/merchandise/

LOC General Director Slawek Krankowski

EMA President Walentina Fedjuschina
